The administrative body shall attach the following forms to the back of the original and each copy of an administrative regulation:
Regulatory impact analysis as required by KRS 13A.240;
Tiering statement as required by KRS 13A.210;
Fiscal note as required by KRS 13A.250;
Federal mandate comparison, if applicable, as required by KRS 13A.245; and
The summaries provided for in KRS 13A.2245, 13A.2251, or 13A.2255, if applicable.
